media:group.media:title: Why should she pick you??? Dating Advice Discord Server
media:group.media:description:
What do you have to offer a woman? Are you sure being alone isn't a consequence of your inadequacies? Modern women aren't any worse than modern men however while women are becoming more entitled, men are becoming weaker. Let's see how Kaivin Seishmule dismantles a man in front of his girlfriend.
